This week I was like, no, use this function. And it was like, no, no, no, I'm not going to

00:27:56.040 --> 00:27:59.560
use that function. I'm going to use one that doesn't exist. And I'm like, no, really use the

00:27:59.560 --> 00:28:00.920
function. That's what I'm trying to write.

00:28:01.479 --> 00:28:07.959
Yes. Thank you so much, Sam, for that fantastic question. And the next one that I have on my

00:28:07.959 --> 00:28:13.640
radar here is an anonymous one. I will read it for our wonderful anonymous asker. It says,

00:28:13.640 --> 00:28:20.119
I've found myself leaning towards development and software engineering within my data science role,

00:28:20.119 --> 00:28:24.119
