00:53:36.139 --> 00:53:40.540
that comes with maybe a smaller sphere of influence. Or if I want to have influence,

00:53:40.540 --> 00:53:46.860
it needs to happen in other ways by writing books or whatever. I'm totally happy with that.

00:53:46.939 --> 00:53:53.820
And if it limits like how high I can go in some org chart, I'm also totally okay with that.

